title: Raphel Warnock Interview, Rihanna New Heat, Part 2 RTL 305, Things 2 B Unseen and more.
itunes:title: Raphel Warnock Interview, Rihanna New Heat, Part 2 RTL 305, Things 2 B Unseen and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride!  Rumors of terrible sex is keeping a woman unsure about dating a specific man.  Senator Raphael Warnock from Georgia stops by the show to discuss the importance of our vote for the midterm elections, the Medicaid cap, computer chips and more.  Finally RiRi got some new music.  Tonight baby is the sequel to the finale of Ready to Love MIA!  Pimpin' is in to give us his NFL week 8 picks.  Today we wrap up with the fellas sharing with us memories that are burned in their brain.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
